{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "第七回\"毒剑常笑\"。安子豪清晨来访王风，告知两件事：一是李大娘不愿王风留在此地；二是四大名捕中的\"毒剑\"常笑即将到达。常笑出身峨眉剑派，\"夺命十二剑\"已有九成火候，权势远超铁恨，办案宁枉毋纵，声名狼藉。其开路先锋昨夜已遭僵尸所害，常笑今夜必至。王风不为所动，坚持留下寻找铁恨尸体。血奴得知常笑之名亦感震惊，她透露宋妈妈是其奶妈，昨夜被王风所伤。王风与血奴同往探视宋妈妈，宋妈妈虽年迈赤裸却仍能诅咒，生命力惊人。王风趁血奴入内时潜入其香闺搜查。血奴归来后对镜自赏，脱去半边衣饰，换上完整湖水绿衣裳——血鹦鹉的奴才首次穿戴整齐，暗示即将应对比王风和武三爷更难对付的人物：毒剑常笑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你决定留在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "你可以这样回覆李大娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "留多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "最低限度也得寻回我朋友的尸体。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "铁恨已变了僵尸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "无论他变成了什么，都是我朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "他变了僵尸之后是不是也认得你这个朋友？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "据说僵尸只在晚间才出现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "据说是这样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "只要你今夜还留在这里，即使见不到你那位僵尸朋友也应该有机会见到另一只蜘蛛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "四大名捕又来了一个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这一个比铁恨更有名气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "这一个是哪一个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "铁恨向来在南方走动，他奉职北方，却走遍天下，凭我这句话，你总该想到他是哪一个了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "毒剑常笑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "正是毒剑常笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "他走到哪里，那里的人就遭殃，这里相信也不会例外。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "你怎么知道，他一定会来这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "他座下有十三个跟班，都是六扇门中的好手，除了侍候他左右，替他搜集证据之外，还兼任他的开路先锋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "开路先锋已到了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "昨日就到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "遇着僵尸，他想不去那个世界也不成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "那个只剩一滩浓血，一只黑手的官差莫非就是常笑座下十三个跟班之一？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "所以我知道常笑今午不到，今夜必到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "这里的人，只怕真的要遭殃了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "第一个遭殃的，也许是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "莫忘了那具僵尸跟你交朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "speaker_name": "安子豪",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "如果你是个聪明人，在他未到之前最好就赶快离开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_an_zi_hao",
      "text": "我不是个聪明人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我真的不是个聪明人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你都看到了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你这个人实在有几分本领，附近数百里，官阶最高的安子豪，居然大清早就来给你问安。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "不是问安，是警告。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "警告你什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "两件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我可否知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "第一件是李大娘不喜欢我留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "她也不喜欢武镇山留在这里，可是这么多年了，又何曾见她如愿以偿？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "武镇山在这里已生了根，并不易动摇，我不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "不过你也莫忘了凭你的身手，若是不愿走，她未必有让你走的办法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "这我可不敢肯定，我不认识她的人，也不清楚她对待敌人向来采取什么手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "她不是已叫了安子豪穿上官服来迫你离开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "如果就是恐吓的手段，这个人倒也不难应付。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你不受恐吓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她能恐吓我什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "最低限度你还有一条命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你只是一个人，说不定她真的有能力杀了你，难道你连死都不怕？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "给你说对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "要我死的人也不止她一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "还有谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "毒剑常笑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你好像也听过这个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "昨夜那个要开棺材验尸的官差，就是他的开路先锋，所以他今午不到，今夜必到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这就是安子豪警告你的第二件事情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "僵尸是我带来的，那官差死在僵尸手下，我当然亦脱不了干系。毒剑常笑的行事作风向来都是宁枉毋纵。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你要做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "出去一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "就这样子出去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我只不过到隔壁。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我忽然想起该去看一看宋妈妈，昨夜她虽然还可以开声咀咒你，但语声已听出有些不妥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我不过打了她一石头，再在她双膝之间撞了一膝盖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你倒将她打得惨了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "当时我却给吓怕了，浑身的气力最多只剩三成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那已经足够，你应该看出她已有多大年纪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "不过她既然还能开口诅咒我，那一撞相信还不成问题，我只担心那块石头。那是块魔石，就我所见已有四个人在那种石头的一击之下死亡。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你似乎忘记了她是个巫婆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我没有忘记，奇浓嘉嘉普的妖魔最好也没有忘记。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "所以，我非要去看一看她不可了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你对她倒也关心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "她本来是我的奶妈，我是吃她的奶长大的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你也许不知道，她年轻时候也是个美人，混身上下都美得很。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你又准备做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "跟你去看一下那个宋妈妈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你以为她还会高兴见到你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "他本来就不高兴见到我，但我要见她，她还是非要见我不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你还敢再到那个地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "现在是白天，太阳底下不成还有什么妖魔鬼怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那个地方终年不见阳光。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你敢去的地方我为什么不敢去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你像是不高兴我再到那个地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我只是关心你，昨夜你不是给吓得的失魂落魄？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "有过一次经验，就不会再害怕的了。你真的关心我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "假的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我只也不过在想知道那魔石对她有什么影响。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宋妈妈。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "血奴么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "这巫婆的生命力还算强韧。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "姓王的小杂种也来了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她的耳朵的确灵得很。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "天咒你，咒你下地狱，上刀山……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你是不是还想进去？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你又去什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "什么地方也去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "找人，死人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "去找那僵尸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "反正，我是闲着，总要找些事做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "僵尸夜间才出现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "日间也出现，不过出现的是具尸体。只要找到尸体，也许就有办法要他不再变做僵尸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这也好，活阎王既然今夜必到，就算是少了具僵尸，这里也已够热闹的。僵尸已是半个鬼，鬼最喜欢的，据说就是墓地之类的地方，你知不知道这里东面有一大片山坟，西面也有个乱葬岗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "现在知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你最好莫要再惹上其他的冤魂野鬼。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ma_ma",
      "speaker_name": "宋妈妈",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天咒你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    }
